                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gaobiedeying/">子文东</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">与《不只中国木建筑》形式类似，仍然是非常易读又认真的入门好书。以前虽然觉得一些古典木家具好看，却说不出道理，现在终于开始明白了些门道。好想再去国博看一次传统家具展啊。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="619186281">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-619186281" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-619186281" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="619186281">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4268425/">穆清</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-12-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一年级木工课时候看的，小图特别逗！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

