  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2437666">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2437666/" class="title-link">家具史就是身体史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2437666"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2243972/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2243972-19.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2243972/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">芯存者</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-10-01"
      class="main-meta">2009-10-01 19:10:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2437666_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       有个问题说：什么动物离不开椅子。答案是老总。因为老总如果只能站着，那就成交通警察了。可见椅子对于一个民族的身份养成是多么重要。我以为赵广超的这本《一章木椅》，终于找到了一个词：国家艺术，总算把聚集在“文物”“古物”“古董”“典当”“珍宝”等周边的尘埃都...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            三聯書店（香港）有限公司2007版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
